detail_desc: Long jumper in a soft knit containing some wool with a wide, ribbed polo neck and low dropped shoulders. Long, wide sleeves with ribbed cuffs and ribbing at the hem with slits in the sides. Slightly longer at the back.
Cropped sports top in fast-drying functional fabric with long sleeves and a double-layered trim at the hem with a wrapover at the front.
V-neck T-shirt in premium cotton jersey.
Push-up bra in lace and mesh with underwired, moulded, padded cups for a larger bust and fuller cleavage. Narrow, adjustable shoulder straps and a narrow hook-and-eye fastening at the back.
CONSCIOUS EXCLUSIVE. Earrings in metal and recycled plastic with polished stones at the top and a ball-shaped pendant decorated with beads. Length 6 cm.
Short-sleeved dresses in soft, organic cotton jersey with a round neckline and a seam with a wide flounce at the hem.
Scarf in a soft weave with fringes on the short sides.
Long-sleeved, off-the-shoulder jumper in a fluffy knit with a sheen. Elastication at the top and ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
Straight-style top in an airy rib knit with a round neckline, dropped shoulders, short sleeves and high slits in the sides.
Belt with two rows of metal eyelets and a metal buckle. Width 4 cm.
Short-sleeved, knee-length dress in stretch jersey crêpe with a wrapover V-neck, seam at the waist and bell-shaped skirt. Unlined.
Socks in a soft jacquard knit containing some wool.

Shirt in a striped viscose weave with a grandad collar, French front and yoke with a pleat at the back. Long sleeves with buttoned cuffs and a rounded hem. Slightly longer at the back. Slim fit with narrow shoulders and a tapered waist for a fitted silhouette.
Short, fitted skirt in soft jersey with an elasticated waist and diagonal drawstring.
Canvas hi-tops with a hook and loop fastening and lacing at the front, and a loop at the back. Mesh linings and insoles and rubber soles.
Romper suit in soft, fine-knit cotton with long raglan sleeves with buttons on one shoulder and long legs with buttons from the crotch to the hems.
Double-layered hat in printed jersey.
Sunglasses with metal frames and UV-protective, tinted lenses.
Bolero in soft, fine-knit cotton with a faceted button at the top and scalloped edges.
Dressing gown in sweatshirt fabric with a hood, long sleeves, tie belt at the waist and narrow ribbing around the front, cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Top in patterned cotton jersey with a narrow ribbed trim around the neckline and short cap sleeves. Rounded and longer at the back.
T-shirt in organic cotton jersey.
Cotton cap with a sweatband in a cotton weave, and elastication at the back.
Round-necked T-shirts in soft jersey.
Top in soft, airy jersey with a V-neck and asymmetric butterfly sleeves.
Blouse in cotton seersucker with a square neckline with elastication and a frill trim and short, elasticated, frill-trimmed sleeves with a decorative bow.
Polo-neck jumper knitted in cotton with long sleeves and ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
Ankle-length trousers in airy denim. High, elasticated waist with pleats and ties, side pockets, fake back pockets and wide, straight legs.
Trainers in imitation leather with a padded edge, lacing at the front and a loop at the back. Mesh linings and insoles and patterned soles.
Pointelle-knit tights with an elasticated waist.
Briefs in cotton jersey with an elasticated waist, sewn-on bow at the front and lined gusset.
Fitted, polo-neck top in soft viscose jersey.
Gloves in a soft, fine knit with ribbed cuffs. The tops of the thumb and index finger are in touchscreen-compatible material.
Short, off-the-shoulder dress in sturdy stretch jersey with an elasticated neckline, an elasticated seam at the waist and flared skirt. Flounce at the top and hem. Longer at the back.
Shorts in lightweight sweatshirt fabric with covered elastication and a drawstring at the waist. The cotton content of the shorts is organic.
Sandals in imitation leather with a hook and loop fastening at one side and a loop at the back. Imitation leather linings and insoles and thermoplastic rubber (TPR) soles.
Cropped, short-sleeved T-shirt in cotton piqué with a ribbed collar and zip at the front.
Calf-length dress in glossy satin with a V-neck, adjustable spaghetti shoulder straps and a double-layered wrapover bodice that ties at the back.
Dress in fine-knit cotton with sequined embroidery on the front, long sleeves and a flared skirt.

Ankle-length trousers in woven fabric with a high paper bag waist with pleats and a detachable tie belt. Zip fly with concealed hook-and-eye fasteners, side pockets and straight-cut legs that taper to the hem.
Trousers in viscose jersey with an elasticated waist, side pockets and straight, wide legs.

Sturdy bag in imitation leather with one shorter shoulder strap in imitation leather and one longer, metal chain shoulder strap. Both straps are detachable. Flap with a snap lock at the front. The bag is divided into two sections, one of which fastens with a press-stud and the other with a zip. One inner compartment. Unlined. Size 7.5x15x23 cm.
Short, fitted dress in a patterned viscose weave with a stand-up collar and puff sleeves, concealed zip at the back with concealed hooks and eyes at the top, and a seam at the waist. Jersey lining.
Short, fitted dress with a deep V-neck, concealed zip at the back, half-length puff sleeves and narrow cuffs with adjustable buttoning.
Ankle boots in imitation suede with a zip in the side, loop at the back and gold-coloured trim around the soles. Woven linings and insoles and rubber soles. Heel 2 cm.

Kangol x H&M. Knee-length, padded puffer jacket with a stand-up collar, padded hood, two-way zip down the front and welt pockets at the top. Long sleeves, one with the Kangol logo at the top, and concealed elastication at the cuffs. Recycled polyester lining.
Hat knitted in soft cashmere with a roll edge.
Imitation leather purse with a zip around the top, card slots and a zipped coin compartment. Lined. Size 2x10x19.5 cm.
Hi-tops in imitation leather and mesh with a padded shaft, adjustable hook and loop tab, elasticated lacing and a loop at the back. Pile linings and insoles and rubber soles.
Swim top and swim shorts in UV-protective fabric. Top with long raglan sleeves and a small stand-up collar. Shorts with an elasticated drawstring waist and lined front. UPF 50.
Top in soft, organic cotton jersey with long raglan sleeves in a contrasting colour.
Thong briefs in lace and mesh with a low waist, lined gusset, wide sides and string back.
Dress in woven fabric with a sheen. Deep V-neck, a concealed zip in one side, a seam at the waist and a skirt with pleats.

Short dress in an airy, patterned cotton poplin weave with a deep neckline at the front and an opening with a button at the back of the neck. Short puff sleeves with narrow elastication, a seam at the waist and a flared skirt. Lined at the top.
Shorts in soft, washed cotton twill with an elasticated drawstring waist, fake fly, side pockets and a welt back pocket.
Short-sleeved cotton jersey top in a relaxed fit with a slightly wider neckline and a rounded hem.
Long-sleeved jumper in a knit containing some wool with a motif on the front and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Double-layered hat in soft jersey with a text print and reversible sequins on the front.
Two-strand, thin metal chain necklace with one small, round pendant and one rectangular pendant with a marbled plastic bead. Adjustable length 41-48 cm.
Sleeveless, V-neck jumpsuit in fast-drying functional fabric with details in ventilating mesh. Low cut with horizontal straps at the back, and ankle-length legs.

Pyjamas in soft viscose jersey and lace. V-neck top with triangular lace cups, narrow, adjustable shoulder straps, and concealed elastication and a lace trim under the bust. Shorts with an elasticated waist and lace trim at the hems.
5-pocket jeans in soft, washed denim with an all-over print, adjustable elasticated waist and fly with a press-stud.
Metal rings in various sizes and designs.
Jacket in woven fabric with a satin shawl collar and welt front pockets. No fasteners. Lined.
Thin metal chain anklets, one with plastic beads and two with metal pendants. Adjustable length 22-25.5 cm.
Padded jacket with a high stand-up collar, zip and wind flap with press-studs down the front, pockets in the side seams and a concealed drawstring at the hem.
Shorts in stretch, matt silk cotton twill with a zip fly and concealed hook-and-eye fastener. Side pockets, welt back pockets with a button and sewn-in turn-ups at the hems.
Large make-up bag with a zip at the top. Lined. Size 18x25 cm.
Hat knitted in a soft wool, alpaca and nylon blend with a wide, ribbed hem.
T-shirt in cotton jersey with a print motif. Ribbing around the neckline.
Pyjamas in soft jersey. Wide, short-sleeved top with a print motif on the front. Short, patterned shorts with an elasticated waist.
Short necklace with fabric-covered beads. Adjustable length 45-57 cm.
Wide sports top in fast-drying slub jersey made from a viscose and modal blend with low dropped shoulders and short sleeves.
5-pocket, slim-fit, knee-length shorts in washed stretch denim with a print motif on the legs, adjustable elasticated waist and zip fly and button.
Trainers in fabric with imitation leather details, a lightly padded edge and tongue, elasticated lacing at the front and a small loop at the back. Patterned soles with a good grip.

Padded parka in woven fabric with a fleece-lined, drawstring hood and zip with a wind flap and press-studs down the front. Flap chest and front pockets with a pleat and button, a concealed drawstring at the waist and an adjustable hook and loop tab at the cuffs. Lined.
V-neck tunic in airy cotton voile. Small stand-up collar with gathers and a drawstring, short raglan sleeves and short slits in the sides.
Scarf in a soft jacquard weave with fringes on the short sides.
Short-sleeved bodysuit in soft, printed organic cotton jersey with an opening and press-studs at one side and press-studs at the crotch.
Sleeveless nursing tops in organic cotton jersey with a wrapover at the top and practical inner top for easier nursing access.
